	include/libssh2.h, src/Makefile.am, src/version.c:
	- Added libssh2_version()

2009-02-20  Daniel Stenberg

	* NEWS, src/channel.c:
	- (Feb 20 2009) libssh2_channel_direct_tcpip_ex() bug #1902169
	  fixed, which caused it to fail when called a second time.

2009-02-17  dottedmag

	* docs/libssh2_base64_decode.3: Fixed dash-as-minus warning in
	libssh2_base64_decode.3 manpage

2009-02-17  dottedmag

	* docs/libssh2_banner_set.3: Fixed syntax error in
	libssh2_banner_set.3 manpage

2009-02-16  Simon Josefsson <simon@josefsson.org>

	* src/Makefile.am: Bump ABI revision from 1.0.0 to 1.0.1 due to
	code changes.

2009-02-16  Simon Josefsson <simon@josefsson.org>

	* include/libssh2.h: Fix typo.

2009-02-16  Simon Josefsson <simon@josefsson.org>

	* NEWS: Add date for v1.0 release.

2009-02-12  Daniel Stenberg

	* NEWS, src/channel.c:
	- (Feb 12 2009) Romain Bondue extended Markus Moeller fix from Feb
	  8, based on a previous (uncommitted) patch by Erik Brossler. It
	  improves libssh2_channel_write_ex in blocking situations when the
	  socket is set non- blocking.

2009-02-08  Daniel Stenberg

	* NEWS, src/channel.c: Markus Moeller fixed a flaw in
	libssh2_channel_write_ex() that would occur on EAGAIN situations.

2009-01-01  Daniel Stenberg

	* TODO: I want to remove all those macros from the official API at
	next soname bump

2009-01-01  Daniel Stenberg

	* src/kex.c, src/scp.c, tests/ssh2.c: fixed compiler warnings, and
	stripped off "libssh2_" from static functions as that makes shorter
	function names and then making the code look fine within 80 columns
	is easier!

2009-01-01  Daniel Stenberg

	* include/libssh2.h, include/libssh2_publickey.h,
	include/libssh2_sftp.h: made the three public headers use (mostly)
	lines shorter than 80 columns as HACKING says - it makes them much
	more readable to my old tired eyes...

2008-12-28  Daniel Stenberg

	* include/libssh2.h: we're actually working on the 1.0.1 version
	now (or should it be 1.1?)

