	errors in libssh2_sftp_init and libssh2_sftp_open_ex manpages.

2007-11-18   Guenter Knauf

	* src/kex.c, src/sftp.c: fixed 'uninitialized' compiler warnings.

2007-11-12  Daniel Stenberg

	* src/userauth.c: valgrind was friendly enough to point out that
	doing memcpy() on overlapping memory areas is a very bad idea so I
	changed this to memmove()

