2007-06-13   James Housley

	* docs/libssh2_channel_forward_accept.3,
	docs/libssh2_channel_forward_listen_ex.3,
	docs/libssh2_channel_set_blocking.3,
	docs/libssh2_channel_wait_eof.3, docs/libssh2_poll.3,
